#

Fish Tacos with Cilantro Lime Sauce

25 min
$15
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

fishdairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-protein

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main

Tags:

easyfreshtacosseafood

Description

Deliciously seasoned fish wrapped in warm tortillas, topped with a zesty cilantro lime sauce for a refreshing bite.

Ingredients

  • white fish fillets (such as tilapia or cod): 1 pound
  • corn tortillas: 8
  • cabbage, shredded: 2 cups
  • avocado, sliced: 1
  • lime, juiced: 2
  • cilantro, chopped: 1/4 cup
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
